    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation to the author's intent in its original canonical context. The four movements below trace the chapter's argument from each leadership indictment to Micah's climactic verdict, setting each oracle in its historical, covenantal, and canonical context. Where Hebrew terminology sharpens the meaning, a note follows the exposition.",
